    <item>
      <title>特朗普寻求结束与保守派的“不和”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/trump-seeks-end-to-discord-with-stark-conservative-vision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普将在遭遇暗杀未遂后的首次公开讲话中呼吁结束美国社会的“不和与分裂”，同时阐述保守派的愿景，誓言驱逐非法移民并恢复“法律和秩序”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/trump-seeks-end-to-discord-with-stark-conservative-vision</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 02:11:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乔恩·泰斯特成为最新一位敦促拜登退出竞选的民主党人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/jon-tester-becomes-latest-democrat-urging-biden-to-leave-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们越来越担心总统将无法在 11 月击败唐纳德·特朗普，蒙大拿州的乔恩·泰斯特成为最新一位呼吁乔·拜登退出竞选的参议院民主党人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/jon-tester-becomes-latest-democrat-urging-biden-to-leave-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 01:23:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Yoma 董事长与缅甸当局沟通受限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/yoma-chairman-with-myanmar-authorities-communication-restricted</link>
      <description><![CDATA[缅甸富豪之一 Serge Pun 目前住在缅甸有关部门“提供的住所，并得到相关部门的配合”，Yoma Strategic Holdings Ltd. 周四表示。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/yoma-chairman-with-myanmar-authorities-communication-restricted</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 01:19:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>无论民主党候选人如何，共和党人都对特朗普赢得 2024 年大选充满信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/republicans-confident-in-chances-regardless-of-democratic-ticket</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登的政党陷入了是否要逼迫这位 81 岁的总统下台的混乱之中。共和党人有一个明确的观点：这并不重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/republicans-confident-in-chances-regardless-of-democratic-ticket</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 01:12:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝韩边境紧张局势加剧，金正恩会见俄罗斯军事特使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/kim-jong-un-meets-russian-military-envoys-as-korean-border-tensions-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着朝韩边境紧张局势升级，朝鲜领导人金正恩会见了访问平壤的俄罗斯军事代表团，标志着双方安全关系的深化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/kim-jong-un-meets-russian-military-envoys-as-korean-border-tensions-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 00:05:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登内阁成员讨论他是否应该结束竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/some-biden-cabinet-members-discussed-if-time-for-him-to-end-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，总统乔·拜登的一些内阁成员曾私下讨论过，现在是否是时候让他最亲密的顾问与他一起考虑他日益黯淡的选举前景了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/some-biden-cabinet-members-discussed-if-time-for-him-to-end-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 23:57:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登面临越来越多的猜测和放弃竞选的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/biden-fine-campaign-insists-as-pressure-to-drop-out-mounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，总统乔·拜登对民主党总统候选人提名的把握似乎正在下滑，因为他在特拉华州海滨别墅因感染新冠肺炎而隔离期间，正在权衡党内高层议员越来越多地公开发出的警告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/biden-fine-campaign-insists-as-pressure-to-drop-out-mounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 15:38:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜向韩国发射可能携带垃圾的气球</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-18/urgent-north-korea-launches-balloons-likely-carrying-trash-toward-south-korea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首尔，韩国（美联社）——韩国周五表示，已恢复向朝鲜发射宣传广播，以报复朝鲜最新一轮发射携带垃圾的气球的行为，这种重启冷战式战术的做法正在加剧两个对手之间的敌意。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-18/urgent-north-korea-launches-balloons-likely-carrying-trash-toward-south-korea</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:01:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平的重要经济会议表明党准备应对经济放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/china-vows-to-push-for-high-quality-development-as-top-mission</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平誓言要让“高质量发展”成为世界第二大经济体的指导力量，但这并没有什么初步迹象表明，最高领导层正准备采取重大措施刺激需求或遏制房地产市场低迷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/china-vows-to-push-for-high-quality-development-as-top-mission</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 08:35:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰两辆载有中国游客的巴士偏离道路 15 人受伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-18/buses-carrying-chinese-tourists-veer-off-new-zealand-road-in-2-crashes-at-the-same-spot-15-hurt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠灵顿，新西兰（美联社）——周四，两辆载有中国游客的大巴在新西兰南岛的恶劣天气条件下偏离同一段道路，15 名乘客被送往医院，其中两人受重伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-18/buses-carrying-chinese-tourists-veer-off-new-zealand-road-in-2-crashes-at-the-same-spot-15-hurt</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 03:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
